A non-self-guiding tutorial for programmers new to C.

    Corollary 1:
        If you are new to programming,
        then this tutorial is not for you.

    Corollary 2:
        If you are seeking a linear walkthrough of topics,
        then this tutorial is not for you.

This tutorial is free and open.

    Corollary 1:
        If you wish to use, modify, redistribute, or sell copies,
        then see COPYING for license.

    Corollary 2:
        If you find anything wrong or confusing,
        then do complain and/or submit fixes.
